    "DEV-22 Integrated CNN The proposed CADx system employs DenseNet-201 27, 28, EfficientNetB7 29, and VGG-19 30 for disease diagnosis, as each of the three has its advantages.",
    "Due to its dense connectivity, DenseNet-201 is capable of extracting a vast array of features, while EfficientNetB7 offers an appropriate level of complexity, and VGG-19 provides additional depth to retrieve supplementary information.",
    "Thanks to this integration, the system can now provide plausible solutions for both common and complex cases of colorectal colonoscopy images, including the general structure and texture.",
    "Figure 5 illustrates the architecture of the DEV-22 Integrated CNN.",
    "This means that the proposed PolynetDWTCADx system is better at diagnosing and separating things into groups than other models for looking at medical images of colorectal cancer."
